      "description": "REGRESSION (cross-tenant leak fix): a bare `user` role must NOT read a user record it does not own in another tenant. Previously own_resource listed roles:[\"user\"] alongside the derived role, and Cerbos ORs them — so the bare role bypassed the owner+tenant scoping. Now own_resource (derived-role only) requires P.id==owner_id AND same tenant.",
